{
  "_doc": "Central agent registry v2 — committed TEMPLATE (placeholders only, no PII). COPY to shared/registry.json and fill in real jids / owner phone; registry.json is gitignored. This v2 registry is the COMPLETE single source of truth for WhatsApp wiring: openclaw.json's whatsapp groups, bindings, agents.list identity, and cron delivery targets are all DERIVED from it by shared/tools/registry-sync.mjs (--check / --apply). agent-registry.mjs loads registry.json if present else this example. workspaceDir/configPath/roster paths are repo-relative and resolved to absolute by the loader (which derives the repo root from its own module location; set \"_repoRoot\" to override). --- v2 SCHEMA --- top-level `groups`: symbolic-name -> { jid, label(human), requireMention, listenOnly?, routeAgentId?, systemPrompt? }. Per-agent: `primaryGroup`+`groups` are SYMBOLIC names -> resolved to jids (primaryGroupId/groupIds); `identity`{name(Hebrew wake-word/display), emoji, mentionPatterns?(default [name])}; `cronTargets`{default:<symbolic>, <cron-job-name>:<symbolic>}; `listenGroups`(symbolic) = listenOnly groups this agent OWNS. listenOnly groups stay OUT of any agent's `groups`; the silent `listener` agent (empty groups, unmatchable mentionPatterns) is the route target and is excluded from listAgents() by default. Optional per-agent blocks: sessionHygiene, selfEdit {guardedJson,coreTool}, chatLog {labels,e164DigitsOnly,classifyScout,media,legacyBotNames,sheetMirror}, ackReact {enabled(def true), scope:'mentions'(def)|'all'}. owner {e164,label} lives ONCE at top level. --- ARCHIVED (retirement) --- an agent (or a top-level group) with `archived: true` is RETIRED: kept here for a future revival but excluded from listAgents()/getAgent()/getGroups()/byGroup by default (pass {includeArchived:true} to reach it), and registry-sync REMOVES its openclaw.json allowlist/binding/agents.list wiring (--check flags it, --apply drops it). To REVIVE: flip archived→false, move the workspace back, `registry-sync --apply`, re-enable its systemd timer + restart the gateway. (pitzi/pitzi-demo below are archived — the nuts-shop demo bot, retired 2026-07-17; workspace lives in archive/workspace-pitzuchim.)",
